# Style for the hand-written C-ABI emscripten mesh-parser sources
# (src/core/loaders/wasm/collada_mesh_parser.cpp, obj_parser.cpp).
# Apply with:  clang-format -i src/core/loaders/wasm/*.cpp
# These files are single translation units by design and are exempt from the
# JS/TS line/size budgets — see docs/architecture.md §11 and docs/wasm-build.md.
---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: Google
Standard: c++17
IndentWidth: 2
ColumnLimit: 100
